divs: Sighting DetailsON HOLIDAYS, I CONTINUE MY SEARCH FOR UFOS. INSTALLED MY CANON POWERSHOT S80 CAMERA ON A TRIPOD TO FILM FOR 3-4 MINUTES AT THE LANDSCAPE AT A FILM SPEED OF 15 FPS. THIS IS THE CLEAREST SIGHTING MADE OF MANY MADE IN SANTIAGO, CHILE AFTER FOLLOWING THE SAME PROCESS OF FILMING TO THE LANDSCAPE. THERE ARE MANY MORE BACKING UP THIS TYPE OF SIGHTINGS. THE VIDEO CLIP IS ALSO AVAILABLE (200 MB), THE JPG IMAGE BELONGS TO A SCREENSHOT OF THE FILM. I WAIT FOR COMMENTS AND FUTURE SHARING OF IDEAS... JORGE
